          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Accuracy in Medicare Physician Payment Act of 2015 </b></p> <p> Amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to direct the Department of Health and Human Services to establish and appoint an expert outside advisory panel for purposes of providing oversight to the processes relating to valuation of physicians' services.</p>]]></text>
